lyrics:
(Verse 1)
Mike and Randy, down at Agdaze,
Ring tossing, crane playing in a mad daze,
There they saw her, Marcia Yockey,
Weather queen, looking all cocky

(Chorus)
But when they asked for a shout-out, loud,
Marcia's face fell in a weather cloud,
"Can't mention names," she said with a frown,
"FCC rules, gotta keep 'em down."
